   Strange lights and evil auras have been observed near the dark temple of
Qazaash and many speak fearfully of the return of that dark god. If this
indeed comes to pass, unspeakable disasters will befall Darkwind. One
person alone may know the cause, and, more pertinently, the solution to
this danger. Seek out the hierophant druid in the refuge he went to
after his defeat by the evil followers of Qazaash. With him may lie
Darkwind's only chance.

   This is a hard quest meant for high level players. It requires the
killing of several deadly monsters, but also the wisdom to avoid impossible
combats. Take care and much grief may be avoided.
   This quest is only solvable once per reboot.
